svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p>Numbers for 26-64 transaction clusters, benchmarking all of the clusters:</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/original/2X/2/2fe344f4d51f18a5a7406daa4e411fe84afed437.png\" data-download-href=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/2fe344f4d51f18a5a7406daa4e411fe84afed437\" title=\"clusters_sim2023_min\"><img src=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/2/2fe344f4d51f18a5a7406daa4e411fe84afed437_2_227x142.png\" alt=\"clusters_sim2023_min\" data-base62-sha1=\"6PDmxbkv8Vsr1lf7nJyIbNtxQkD\" width=\"227\" height=\"142\" srcset=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/2/2fe344f4d51f18a5a7406daa4e411fe84afed437_2_227x142.png, https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/2/2fe344f4d51f18a5a7406daa4e411fe84afed437_2_340x213.png 1.5x, https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/2/2fe344f4d51f18a5a7406daa4e411fe84afed437_2_454x284.png 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"FBFBFB\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">clusters_sim2023_min</span><span class=\"informations\">1280\u00d7800 81.2 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/original/2X/d/d23c74c16f23e5598d6f59ced6f6a0a48616c5b5.png\" data-download-href=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/d23c74c16f23e5598d6f59ced6f6a0a48616c5b5\" title=\"clusters_sim2023_avg\"><img src=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/d/d23c74c16f23e5598d6f59ced6f6a0a48616c5b5_2_227x142.png\" alt=\"clusters_sim2023_avg\" data-base62-sha1=\"tZPNji1C1cbz9XGK5jMKLKP5EW1\" width=\"227\" height=\"142\" srcset=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/d/d23c74c16f23e5598d6f59ced6f6a0a48616c5b5_2_227x142.png, https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/d/d23c74c16f23e5598d6f59ced6f6a0a48616c5b5_2_340x213.png 1.5x, https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/d/d23c74c16f23e5598d6f59ced6f6a0a48616c5b5_2_454x284.png 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"FBFBFB\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">clusters_sim2023_avg</span><span class=\"informations\">1280\u00d7800 76.2 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/original/2X/9/9859d8515199ad0062c21cdacc97afe811d21811.png\" data-download-href=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/9859d8515199ad0062c21cdacc97afe811d21811\" title=\"clusters_sim2023_max\"><img src=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/9/9859d8515199ad0062c21cdacc97afe811d21811_2_227x142.png\" alt=\"clusters_sim2023_max\" data-base62-sha1=\"lJL4bwjK6wa4XkfPz5DCi1fwNFf\" width=\"227\" height=\"142\" srcset=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/9/9859d8515199ad0062c21cdacc97afe811d21811_2_227x142.png, https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/9/9859d8515199ad0062c21cdacc97afe811d21811_2_340x213.png 1.5x, https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/9/9859d8515199ad0062c21cdacc97afe811d21811_2_454x284.png 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"FBFBFB\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">clusters_sim2023_max</span><span class=\"informations\">1280\u00d7800 73.5 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p>For sufficiently large clusters, and in average and maximum runtime, SFL is the clear winner in this data set. CSS has better lower bounds, but is terrible in the worst case (31.5 ms).</p>\n<h3><a name=\"p-4854-randomly-generated-spanning-tree-clusters-3\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-4854-randomly-generated-spanning-tree-clusters-3\"></a>Randomly-generated spanning-tree clusters</h3>\n<p>In this dataset, for each size between 26 and 64 transactions, 100 random spanning-tree clusters (i.e., a connected graph with exactly n-1 dependencies) were generated, like this 64-transaction one:</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/original/2X/c/cfe0c1b36089028a85a14f08dd8639b98e70c4fe.png\" data-download-href=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/cfe0c1b36089028a85a14f08dd8639b98e70c4fe\" title=\"spanning\"><img src=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/c/cfe0c1b36089028a85a14f08dd8639b98e70c4fe_2_690x173.png\" alt=\"spanning\" data-base62-sha1=\"tEYngxsf8LUCo8HLISq7aXaYPIG\" width=\"690\" height=\"173\" srcset=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/c/cfe0c1b36089028a85a14f08dd8639b98e70c4fe_2_690x173.png, https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/c/cfe0c1b36089028a85a14f08dd8639b98e70c4fe_2_1035x259.png 1.5x, https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/c/cfe0c1b36089028a85a14f08dd8639b98e70c4fe_2_1380x346.png 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"F7F7F7\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">spanning</span><span class=\"informations\">2899\u00d7731 274 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/original/2X/5/5bb80adeed17b51cc40db04bb8d0dd33c1f7982d.png\" data-download-href=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/5bb80adeed17b51cc40db04bb8d0dd33c1f7982d\" title=\"clusters_spanning_min\"><img src=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/5/5bb80adeed17b51cc40db04bb8d0dd33c1f7982d_2_227x142.png\" alt=\"clusters_spanning_min\" data-base62-sha1=\"d5nL3ubMjye46VCC7PzkWAjQtxH\" width=\"227\" height=\"142\" srcset=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/5/5bb80adeed17b51cc40db04bb8d0dd33c1f7982d_2_227x142.png, https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/5/5bb80adeed17b51cc40db04bb8d0dd33c1f7982d_2_340x213.png 1.5x, https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/5/5bb80adeed17b51cc40db04bb8d0dd33c1f7982d_2_454x284.png 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"FBFBFB\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">clusters_spanning_min</span><span class=\"informations\">1280\u00d7800 81.5 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/original/2X/8/8dbef4627f2752871030031adb23b0146ab3659d.png\" data-download-href=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/8dbef4627f2752871030031adb23b0146ab3659d\" title=\"clusters_spanning_avg\"><img src=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/8/8dbef4627f2752871030031adb23b0146ab3659d_2_227x142.png\" alt=\"clusters_spanning_avg\" data-base62-sha1=\"kdWro2g2uT1bdQMlGQErc81ILjn\" width=\"227\" height=\"142\" srcset=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/8/8dbef4627f2752871030031adb23b0146ab3659d_2_227x142.png, https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/8/8dbef4627f2752871030031adb23b0146ab3659d_2_340x213.png 1.5x, https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/8/8dbef4627f2752871030031adb23b0146ab3659d_2_454x284.png 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"FBFBFB\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">clusters_spanning_avg</span><span class=\"informations\">1280\u00d7800 71.8 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/original/2X/d/d2c7dc87d02029080ee04797056e063aafe7398e.png\" data-download-href=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/d2c7dc87d02029080ee04797056e063aafe7398e\" title=\"clusters_spanning_max\"><img src=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/d/d2c7dc87d02029080ee04797056e063aafe7398e_2_227x142.png\" alt=\"clusters_spanning_max\" data-base62-sha1=\"u4Et8z6mIRRemy47v1N25OjxlW6\" width=\"227\" height=\"142\" srcset=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/d/d2c7dc87d02029080ee04797056e063aafe7398e_2_227x142.png, https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/d/d2c7dc87d02029080ee04797056e063aafe7398e_2_340x213.png 1.5x, https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/d/d2c7dc87d02029080ee04797056e063aafe7398e_2_454x284.png 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"FBFBFB\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">clusters_spanning_max</span><span class=\"informations\">1280\u00d7800 77.1 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p>Again, SFL seems the clear winner.</p>\n<h3><a name=\"p-4854-randomly-generated-medium-density-clusters-4\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-4854-randomly-generated-medium-density-clusters-4\"></a>Randomly-generated medium-density clusters</h3>\n<p>In this dataset, for each size between 26 and 64 transactions, 100 random spanning-tree clusters (with roughly 3 dependencies per transaction) were generated, like this 64-transaction one. I promise this is not the plot of <a href=\"https://xkcd.com/657/\">Primer (2004)</a>:</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/original/2X/1/1bb2ca8e1c19a0bd2356b79ae7c75ec3928e68f3.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/1bb2ca8e1c19a0bd2356b79ae7c75ec3928e68f3\" title=\"medium\"><img src=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/1/1bb2ca8e1c19a0bd2356b79ae7c75ec3928e68f3_2_690x216.jpeg\" alt=\"medium\" data-base62-sha1=\"3X1WUmO6VnMeUpxpLBoBePwqWGf\" width=\"690\" height=\"216\" srcset=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/1/1bb2ca8e1c19a0bd2356b79ae7c75ec3928e68f3_2_690x216.jpeg, https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/1/1bb2ca8e1c19a0bd2356b79ae7c75ec3928e68f3_2_1035x324.jpeg 1.5x, https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/1/1bb2ca8e1c19a0bd2356b79ae7c75ec3928e68f3_2_1380x432.jpeg 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"EFEFEF\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">medium</span><span class=\"informations\">4469\u00d71403 1000 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/original/2X/7/795b680e90b1c27af4ebce24ae9f36f583f86dd4.png\" data-download-href=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/795b680e90b1c27af4ebce24ae9f36f583f86dd4\" title=\"clusters_medium_min\"><img src=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/7/795b680e90b1c27af4ebce24ae9f36f583f86dd4_2_227x142.png\" alt=\"clusters_medium_min\" data-base62-sha1=\"hjzBUaRwuFqz5dcIwHQDkZYJPIE\" width=\"227\" height=\"142\" srcset=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/7/795b680e90b1c27af4ebce24ae9f36f583f86dd4_2_227x142.png, https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/7/795b680e90b1c27af4ebce24ae9f36f583f86dd4_2_340x213.png 1.5x, https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/7/795b680e90b1c27af4ebce24ae9f36f583f86dd4_2_454x284.png 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"FBFAFB\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">clusters_medium_min</span><span class=\"informations\">1280\u00d7800 98.8 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/original/2X/f/f6d948751745d0f20ae92e27059b29b19d997728.png\" data-download-href=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/f6d948751745d0f20ae92e27059b29b19d997728\" title=\"clusters_medium_avg\"><img src=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/f/f6d948751745d0f20ae92e27059b29b19d997728_2_227x142.png\" alt=\"clusters_medium_avg\" data-base62-sha1=\"zdIZ2nqb55EtnoqlsPTTFT1cYDS\" width=\"227\" height=\"142\" srcset=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/f/f6d948751745d0f20ae92e27059b29b19d997728_2_227x142.png, https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/f/f6d948751745d0f20ae92e27059b29b19d997728_2_340x213.png 1.5x, https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/f/f6d948751745d0f20ae92e27059b29b19d997728_2_454x284.png 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"FBFBFB\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">clusters_medium_avg</span><span class=\"informations\">1280\u00d7800 73.9 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/original/2X/e/e4943a47484e8c86abee004b30ffc62196b36402.png\" data-download-href=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/e4943a47484e8c86abee004b30ffc62196b36402\" title=\"clusters_medium_max\"><img src=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/e/e4943a47484e8c86abee004b30ffc62196b36402_2_227x142.png\" alt=\"clusters_medium_max\" data-base62-sha1=\"wC6rfAgY2NsJb36vLvZxeCJkQw2\" width=\"227\" height=\"142\" srcset=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/e/e4943a47484e8c86abee004b30ffc62196b36402_2_227x142.png, https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/e/e4943a47484e8c86abee004b30ffc62196b36402_2_340x213.png 1.5x, https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/e/e4943a47484e8c86abee004b30ffc62196b36402_2_454x284.png 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"FBFBFB\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">clusters_medium_max</span><span class=\"informations\">1280\u00d7800 84.3 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p>Notably, SFL performs worst in the worst case here, with up to 83.1 \u03bcs runtime, though even the fastest algorithm (unidirectional GGT) even takes up to 30.2 \u03bcs. This is probably due to it inherently scaling with the number of dependencies.</p>\n<h3><a name=\"p-4854-randomly-generated-complete-bipartite-clusters-5\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-4854-randomly-generated-complete-bipartite-clusters-5\"></a>Randomly-generated complete bipartite clusters</h3>\n<p>In this dataset, for each size between 26 and 64 transactions, 100 random complete-connected bipartite clusters (with roughly n/4 dependencies per transaction) were generated, like this 64-transaction one:</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/original/2X/f/f3fb49bc0ee3785b66f8b0ad997b985e435f18d5.png\" data-download-href=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/f3fb49bc0ee3785b66f8b0ad997b985e435f18d5\" title=\"bipartite\"><img src=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/f/f3fb49bc0ee3785b66f8b0ad997b985e435f18d5_2_690x15.png\" alt=\"bipartite\" data-base62-sha1=\"yOmpgaj0xSIW6UTther0VFFJw0d\" width=\"690\" height=\"15\" srcset=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/f/f3fb49bc0ee3785b66f8b0ad997b985e435f18d5_2_690x15.png, https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/f/f3fb49bc0ee3785b66f8b0ad997b985e435f18d5_2_1035x22.png 1.5x, https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/f/f3fb49bc0ee3785b66f8b0ad997b985e435f18d5_2_1380x30.png 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"A3A3A3\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">bipartite</span><span class=\"informations\">6737\u00d7155 124 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/original/2X/7/7d4502c92ef877672346cda85b7f30212aedc317.png\" data-download-href=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/7d4502c92ef877672346cda85b7f30212aedc317\" title=\"clusters_bipartite_min\"><img src=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/7/7d4502c92ef877672346cda85b7f30212aedc317_2_227x142.png\" alt=\"clusters_bipartite_min\" data-base62-sha1=\"hSbxpGowcPSRGf6RNMeYwu8ZEQ7\" width=\"227\" height=\"142\" srcset=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/7/7d4502c92ef877672346cda85b7f30212aedc317_2_227x142.png, https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/7/7d4502c92ef877672346cda85b7f30212aedc317_2_340x213.png 1.5x, https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/7/7d4502c92ef877672346cda85b7f30212aedc317_2_454x284.png 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"FBFBFB\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">clusters_bipartite_min</span><span class=\"informations\">1280\u00d7800 90.8 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/original/2X/a/aa6b69712fd0da5fa5dd7371c60d989193a6ebee.png\" data-download-href=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/aa6b69712fd0da5fa5dd7371c60d989193a6ebee\" title=\"clusters_bipartite_avg\"><img src=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/a/aa6b69712fd0da5fa5dd7371c60d989193a6ebee_2_227x142.png\" alt=\"clusters_bipartite_avg\" data-base62-sha1=\"ojBiwSihXBJqPDRWdxuY42KUX8O\" width=\"227\" height=\"142\" srcset=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/a/aa6b69712fd0da5fa5dd7371c60d989193a6ebee_2_227x142.png, https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/a/aa6b69712fd0da5fa5dd7371c60d989193a6ebee_2_340x213.png 1.5x, https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/a/aa6b69712fd0da5fa5dd7371c60d989193a6ebee_2_454x284.png 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"FBFBFB\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">clusters_bipartite_avg</span><span class=\"informations\">1280\u00d7800 74.6 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/original/2X/8/8cb7f307405f610d22d90f6c88fd432ae5fa1827.png\" data-download-href=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/8cb7f307405f610d22d90f6c88fd432ae5fa1827\" title=\"clusters_bipartite_max\"><img src=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/8/8cb7f307405f610d22d90f6c88fd432ae5fa1827_2_227x142.png\" alt=\"clusters_bipartite_max\" data-base62-sha1=\"k4QXeSt58pjHoZGYyQNp20GG3s3\" width=\"227\" height=\"142\" srcset=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/8/8cb7f307405f610d22d90f6c88fd432ae5fa1827_2_227x142.png, https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/8/8cb7f307405f610d22d90f6c88fd432ae5fa1827_2_340x213.png 1.5x, https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/8/8cb7f307405f610d22d90f6c88fd432ae5fa1827_2_454x284.png 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"FBFBFB\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">clusters_bipartite_max</span><span class=\"informations\">1280\u00d7800 76.3 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p>With even more dependencies per transaction here, SFL\u2019s weakness is even more visible (up to 114.8 \u03bcs), though it affects GGT too. Note that due to the large number of dependencies, these clusters are expensive too: if all the inputs and outputs are key-path P2TR, then the 64-transaction case needs ~103 kvB in transaction input &amp; output data.</p>\n<h3><a name=\"p-4854-methodology-6\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-4854-methodology-6\"></a>Methodology</h3>\n<p>All of these numbers are constructed by:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Gather a list of N clusters (by replaying mempool data, or randomly generating them).</li>\n<li>For each of the N cluster, do the following 5 times:\n<ul>\n<li>Generate 100 RNG seeds for the linearization algorithm.</li>\n<li>For each RNG seed:\n<ul>\n<li>Benchmark optimal linearization 13 times with the same RNG seed, on an AMD Ryzen 9 5950X system.</li>\n<li>Remember the median of those 13 runs, to weed out variance due to task swapping and other effects).</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Remember the average of those 100 medians, as we care mostly about how long the duration of linearization many clusters at once is, not an individual one. This removes some of the variance caused by individual RNG seeds.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Output the minimum, average, and maximum of those 5N average-of-medians.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>All the data and graphs can be found on <a href=\"https://gist.github.com/sipa/6e21121eaecda0cb33f99cb80ad03766\" class=\"inline-onebox\">Cluster linearization databench plotting code \u00b7 GitHub</a>.</p>",
